source.name: SSMMA Available Land
source.description: This dataset includes Available Land for sale and lease in the Chicago Southland region. This data is a aggregation of listings from Wm C Groebe & Co., Newmark, Knight, and Frank, Simborg, Lee & Associates, and Rofo.com.
